title: Windows 8.1 Pro 32-bit(x86) + KMSPico Activation Key - Original
description:
Windwos 8.1 pro allows you to have installed original prototype of windows 8.1 32-bits operating system, your processor must not support
prefetchw if is used for 32 bits, you must have x64 based processor.

Windows 8.1 Professional | 32-Bit System Requirements:

HDD: 10GB Min / 16 GB Required
RAM: 1 GB Required (32 Bits 1gb / 3gb / 6gb)
Processor: Intel(R) Pentium D 1,00 Ghz or higher
Graphics Drivers: DirectX 9.0/9.0c/ DirectX 11
Information: 32-bits does not require prefetchW support, and you can install it with only 1 gb ram.

Windows 8.1 Professional | 64-Bit System Requirements:

HDD: 12GB Min / 20 GB Required
RAM: 2 GB Required (32 Bits 2gb / 4gb / 8gb)
Processor: Intel(R) Pentium D 1,10 Ghz or higher
Graphics Drivers: DirectX 9.0/9.0c/ DirectX 11
Information: 64-bits requires prefetchW support also you must have 2GB Ram to run win 8.1 pro 64 bits| Required processor : x64 based processor
